♪ Remember?

865
01:26:26,510 --> 01:26:29,520
♪ The way we used to kiss

866
01:26:29,520 --> 01:26:31,520
♪ That's what I miss

867
01:26:31,520 --> 01:26:34,520
♪ So close to me

868
01:26:34,520 --> 01:26:39,530
♪ My precious treasure

869
01:26:39,530 --> 01:26:45,530
♪ I never tought that I would

